      "weather": "overcast",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRIBECA (4) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his superb 25.04 win at Shepparton over 450m. Hard to top on the time from two back. BE UNITED (1) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing third (25.53) and beaten 2.5 lengths over 450m at this track. Can measure up. IT'S BUBBLE TIME (2) tends to drift back and work into the race, charging home into the minors two back before winding up late into third (25.26) in a Grade 5 FIN at Warrnambool last time. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from five starts. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and two minor placings from three starts. Overdue and gets his chance. LILLY ZOOM (6) is a last-start placegetter who will have admirers.",
